During this time, the native of Khasavyurt managed to become a three-time prize-winner of the European championships, the champion of Russia, a master of sports of Russia of international class.
When he stopped getting into our national team, it was time to think about changing citizenship.
For several years, the talented wrestler disappeared from sports.
The triumphant return took place at the Asian Championships in 2016 - Batirov already represented Bahrain, for which he won a gold medal and received a ticket to the Olympics in Rio.
