Dongfeng will bring to Russia crosswan Fengguang 370 and a pickup truck Rich New - site Driving www.zr.ru
Dongfeng Fengguang 370 is a representative of the growing car class in China, combining the advantages of a minivan and crossover.
Another announced Russian premiere is the Rich New pickup.
Many Western firms Moscow International Motor Show this year decided to ignore, so the void of the exhibition halls of the Crocus Expo will be filled by Chinese companies.
In particular, a powerful front will be Dongfeng Motor Corporation, which has great views of the Russian market and intends to offer our motorists a number of interesting new products in the near future.
One of them will be the Dongfeng Fengguang 370 crossbar, which went on sale in China this spring at a price of 55 900 yuan (slightly less than 550 thousand. RUB. at the current course).
Such a price tag is unlikely to shine on Russians, and the question of deliveries to our country is still under discussion.
In China, by the way, the Fengguang 370 in June sales managed to get to 11th place in the list of the best-selling minivans, although due to the large ground clearance (175 mm) and a protective plastic body kit along the lower perimeter of the body, it can be ranked as crossovers.
The crosswane is built on the front-wheel drive platform of the younger model Fengguang 360, the 370th has the same wheelbase of 2725 mm, but the body is slightly longer (4565 mm against 4510 mm), the design is more solid, and the equipment is richer.
The salon is decorated with wooden slabs, but the large vertical touch screen shown in the photo "like Tesla" on the center console was only on the early exhibition copies of the crosswyn, and cars with "music" were sold simpler.
Five of the seven seats easily fold, forming a flat loading platform with a length of 1650 mm, the maximum trunk volume is 1500 liters.
The engine for the Fengguang 370 provides only one - 1.5-liter gasoline "atmosphere" with a capacity of 115 hp, docked with a 5-speed manual gearbox.
The manufacturer is modestly silent about the dynamic qualities of the machine, but promises a sparing budget of the owner an appetite of 6.7 l / 100 km.
The Rich New Pickup is a well-known to the Russians Nissan NP300 Navara of the previous generation, but with a slightly refined design by Chinese stylists.
Despite the obsolete design, this model is still in stable demand among the Chinese consumer as a reliable and unpretentious “workhorse”.
At a similar price, Rich New will certainly interest the Russians, because modern Japanese pickup trucks have become exorbitantly expensive.
Rich New is equipped with two engines to choose from: petrol 2.4 l (137 hp) or a 2.5-liter turbodiesel (116 hp).
The gearbox is only mechanics, the drive is on the rear wheels, but there are modifications with a rigidly connected "front".
There will be a new flagship A9 sedan at the Dongfeng booth, its Russian premiere announced the representative office of the Chinese firm back in June.
Minf-like crossovers in the Chinese market is becoming more and more, one of the latest innovations - Cowin V3 and SWM X7.
Currently, the Russian lineup Dongfeng consists of two models: the S30 sedan and the H30 Cross hatchback.
For seven months of this year, dealers of the Chinese company sold 696 cars in our country.
Notifications for the transport tax will cease to be sent by mail - site Driving www.zr.ru
The tax inspectorate has changed the procedure for sending notices of property taxes.
All Russian car owners are accustomed to the scheme that has not changed for years: in the summer and autumn they receive by mail receipts for the payment of transport tax for the previous year.
However, this year many will not wait for them.
The fact is that the tax inspectorate without too much noise changed the procedure for notifying citizens.
Those who are registered in the "Personal Account of the taxpayer" on the official website of the department nalog.ru, the notifications will come electronically.
The inspection automatically considered such Russians online users and crossed them out of a standard, “paper” mailing.
The innovation will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
Everyone else will still receive the usual letters.
However, the opportunity to return to the old scheme is also available to holders of the account on the site.
To do this, they will have to visit the tax office during August and write a statement.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and more convenient.
The notification will appear in the “personal account” immediately after the compilation, while the letter will go for several days and may completely be lost.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service of the tax inspectorate exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the Agency to seriously save on the mailing list.
On the other hand, the modest news on the website of the inspection is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could register in the “personal account” to receive a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for notifications by mail and, without realizing it, fall into the category of non-payers with all the ensuing consequences.
Access to the "Personal Account of the Taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal goslugi.ru, using an electronic signature or the entry of the login and password specified in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained personally in any department of the tax inspectorate (regardless of the place of registration).
We remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid by December 1.
The notifications began in July.
